@DATABASE "Kokotoni Wilf"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - K - Kokotoni Wilf"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - K
                   ====================================

                               Kokotoni Wilf
                               =============



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(43742,0)"}          43742,0
@{"Immunity      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(28929,8) ZXAMPoke(28934,8) ZXAMPoke(28939,8)"}          28929,8:28934,8:28939,8
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(42214,255)"}          42214,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         The "Lives = x" is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
